{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This copies KZones to your user profile, loads it in KWin, and configures Super+Arrow shortcuts.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 Log out and back in\par}
